  "analysis": "We have identified runtime/shared_heap.c as the likely location of the broken major-heap sweep/free-space run-length compression code. The previous grep output was truncated, and the top of shared_heap.c showed pool freelist macros but not enough of the sweep implementation. We need to inspect the full file in chunks and grep targeted identifiers to find the bug before configuring/building.",
